{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-hydrating-day-cream-50ml","title":"NURME Neroli Hydrating Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eThis moisturizing day cream provides long-lasting hydration for dry and stressed skin throughout the day. A powerful blend of antioxidants and restorative ingredients leaves the skin soft and smooth while helping to prevent signs of aging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, has strong antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, making it beneficial for acne-prone skin and clogged pores. It regulates sebum production, balancing oily skin. Rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil offers anti-aging and anti-acne benefits, reducing inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eThis product is packaged in a recyclable polypropylene airless bottle. The airless packaging prevents air exposure, ensuring microbiological purity and extending the shelf life of natural cosmetics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003eApply to clean skin.  Allow to absorb completely. Can be used under makeup or alone.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua*, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Glycerin**, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Betain**, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate*, Glyceryl Stearate**, Cetearyl Alcohol**, Myristyl Myristate**, Sodium Levulinate**, Panthenol*, Sodium Anisate**, Ascorbyl Palmitate**, Benzyl Alcohol**, Lactic Acid**, Sodium Hyaluronate**, Allantoin*, Sodium Benzoate**, Tocopherol**, Potassium Sorbate**, Xanthan Gum**, Hectorite**, Cellulose**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*, Citrus Aurantium Flower Oil*, Limonene***, Linalool***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e* Natural origin\u003cbr\u003e**Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e***Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915909075271,"sku":null,"price":27.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-hydrating-day-cream-50ml-839981.jpg?v=1739897161","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-neroli-hydrating-day-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}